Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸭川特产饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用问吗  去报仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OPC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个朱比朱比奥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打飞他
